body: "Execute full-repo issue sweep and implement top-priority warning-first runtime plus docs and package metadata fixes.\n\nImplementation scope: (1) runtime warning surfaces in settings/lock/item-store paths, (2) tests covering warning behavior and regression semantics, (3) changelog/package metadata alignment, (4) full verification and closure evidence."
